  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Welcome back.


      Did you find anything on your trip?'
    nextOption: There was a hole in reality that only I could see
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'That does sound strange.


      I''ll have to analyze the data from your PurpleTooth transmitter and see if
      there is a reason why only you could see it.'
    nextOption: I have a purple tooth?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Yes, all the bodies created by the BodyMatic have one.


      It''s a chip in your tooth that allows us to download information directly from
      your brain when you are in range.


      Just don''t wear a tinfoil hat or it will block the signals.'
    nextOption: What's tinfoil?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Nevermind, it probably hasn''t been invented yet in your timeline.


      Anyway, I have an assignment for you.'
    nextOption: Sure, tell me about it
